<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
        <%= title %> | ZORA
    </title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/styles.css" />
    <style>
        .legal-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 10rem auto;
            padding: 0 4%;
            line-height: 2;
            color: #444;
        }

        .legal-content h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: black;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .legal-content h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="middle-nav">
            <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; width: 100px;">
                LEGAL<br>POLICIES</div>
            <div class="brand-main">ZORA</div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
                <a href="/home" class="btn-orange" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;">BACK HOME</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="legal-content">
        <h1>
            <%= title %>
        </h1>

        <p>Last Updated: May 2026</p>

        <h3>1. CORE PRINCIPLES</h3>
        <p>Zora Magazine is dedicated to the ethical preservation of fashion narratives. Our operations are governed by
            transparency, integrity, and a commitment to the global creative community. By accessing our digital
            archive, you agree to uphold our standards of intellectual property and professional conduct.</p>

        <h3>2. EDITORIAL INTEGRITY</h3>
        <p>All content published within the Zora ecosystem is protected by international copyright laws. Unauthorized
            reproduction of our architectural design research or high-fashion photography is strictly prohibited. We
            maintain absolute control over our digital assets to ensure the highest quality of presentation for our
            curators.</p>

        <h3>3. USER CONDUCT</h3>
        <p>We expect our members to engage with the platform in a respectful and constructive manner. Any attempt to
            compromise the security of our archive or misrepresent our editorial voice will result in immediate
            termination of access. We reserve the right to curate our community as strictly as we curate our content.
        </p>

        <h3>4. LIABILITY</h3>
        <p>While we strive for absolute accuracy in our trend reporting and design analysis, Zora Magazine provides content
            for informational and aesthetic purposes. We are not liable for decisions made based on our fashion
            forecasts or architectural critiques.</p>

        <div
            style="margin-top: 8rem; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.8rem; font-style: italic;">
            Questions regarding our legal framework can be directed to submissions@zora.co
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="magazine-footer"
        style="padding: 6rem 4% 4rem 4%; background: white; border-top: var(--border-thin);">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div>
                <div class="brand-main"
                    style="font-size: 8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); letter-spacing: -4px; line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    ZORA</div>
                <p style="max-width: 500px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Zora is a curated fashion magazine dedicated to high-fashion narratives and architectural design
                    research. Established in 2026, we serve as a definitive resource for curators, designers, and
                    historians seeking the intersection of movement and structure.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    EDITION 01</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; line-height: 1.8;">
                    MAY 2026 / NEW YORK CITY<br>
                    PUBLISHED BY MEDIA GROUP<br>
                    PRINTED DIGITALLY WORLDWIDE
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    NAVIGATION</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <a href="/archive" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">FULL ARCHIVE</a><br>
                    <a href="/contact" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">CONTACT US</a><br>
                    <a href="/home" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">BACK TO GRID</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase;">
            &copy; 2026 ZORA MAGAZINE. REDEFINING THE DIGITAL NARRATIVE.
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>